data.description: Welcome to this unique split-level gem nestled in the sought-after Dunham Place subdivision-awaiting your personal touch! The main level boasts a generously sized living room and dining room combination. Revel in the contemporary kitchen cabinets, complemented by newer hardwood floors and appliances. A convenient back door leads to a concrete patio, hot tub, and a spacious yard. On the second level, discover a sprawling master bedroom with private access to the bathroom, accompanied by two additional bedrooms. The lower level is an entertainer's dream, featuring a family room with a stunning fireplace, a laundry room, an additional full-size bedroom, and bathroom. This space is perfect for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories. Notable enhancements include a newer appliances (2022), sump-pump (2021),  Hot tub (2020), siding (2018), gutters (2018), ac-unit (2018),countertops (2016), and the installation of the privacy fence, This property is being sold "As-Is Where-Is and requires a clean-out"  Schedule your showing TODAY!
